{"tid":2343593,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"美國駐華大使館: 立即釋放12港人 被指「犯罪」僅是逃避暴政","createTime":"2020-12-28T05:20:37.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-28T13:13:04.000Z","uid":240362,"like":55,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"8b8003555c516d93caa52ffcf6a132908727d2d3","tid":2343593,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-28T05:20:37.000Z","msg":"美國駐華大使館發表聲明，呼籲中國當局立即釋放12名港人，並容許他們離開內地。<br />\n<br />\n涉嫌偷越邊境在內地被控的12名港人，其中10人的案件下午在深圳鹽田法院開審。聲明表示，12名港人被指的所謂「犯罪」，是逃避暴政，又認為中共將不惜一切，阻止民眾在其他地方尋求自由。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1567433-20201228.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1567433-20201228.htm&d=%2BrTTj2V4oNsvrkryR3gjdyVDAD9kR8TUwRzNJuuVR5U%3D&h=88b7f58d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1567433-20201228.htm&h=63a8b22e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1567433-20201228.htm</a>"},{"pid":"15b1a36c4415581d560f8e22086de645c2fd6103","tid":2343593,"uid":126919,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-28T05:21:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"efbd1d605be30cb35d3b344632e0f937d9c0234a","tid":2343593,"uid":183844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-28T05:21:31.000Z","msg":"推呀"},{"pid":"5486448d8870b793e16333f6202615a2f47f7a5c","tid":2343593,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-28T05:21:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.